{"tid":1970020,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"推背圖 預言 打氣Post","createTime":"2020-04-12T22:41:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T23:14:52.000Z","uid":305349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e8d41761263c70ea5b886a884a1fec530f047659","tid":1970020,"uid":305349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T22:41:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">江胡習武後 江河再從頭</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家信唔信呢？反正我就信喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前三個字已經應驗，分別係江澤民、胡錦濤、習近平。<br />\n<br />\n宜家到<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">武</span></strong></span>，即係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">終蝈武漢肺炎</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信疫情過後，各國將會清算支共。除左武肺之外，支共又有豬瘟、黑死病、天鵝禽流感、蝗禍、仲要國寶熊貓都死埋。結合天時地理人和，種種兇兆都顯示支共亡國之時，將不久矣。江山便會從頭來！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我地嘅運動要繼續堅持落去，上twitter, reddit乜都好，輸出革命，你我有責，配合其他國家嘅反抗，將會事半功倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2020天滅中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />口號唔係叫就得，家陣上網行動最實際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算只係FF，正能量係革命運動一個好重要嘅動力來源<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nP.S. 黑警三萬八Thx, 最好全部染武肺死撚哂佢，或者終身需要訓牀吸氧輔助<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60cebd2bdeeeb2dc346efcdb8a116570ae19b15b","tid":1970020,"uid":13230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T22:46:11.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講多d? <br />\n同埋post 埋source"},{"pid":"e8451ead64627417e9771b830950814e7ab1db9d","tid":1970020,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTim